---
import BuildPlanner from "../lab/BuildPlanner.astro";
---
<section class="lab section" id="lab">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="section-label">04 — The Lab</span>
    <span class="section-rule"></span>
    <a href="/lab" class="section-more" data-hover>Open the lab ↗</a>
  </div>

  <h2 class="section-title reveal">See how<br /><em class="stroke">we think</em></h2>

  <p class="work-intro reveal">
    Don't take "AI-native" on faith — try it. Describe your product in a
    sentence and watch our engine sketch a real build plan: scope, stack,
    a day-by-day timeline and the risks we'd pressure-test. This is the
    <em>Generate</em> step of our process, live.
  </p>

  <BuildPlanner />
</section>
